text: The 2016 southern Taiwan earthquake happened in Taiwan on 6 February 2016. 116 people were killed. The source of the earthquake was in Kaohsiung. ==References== Category:2016 disasters in Asia Category:2016 earthquakes Category:2010s earthquakes in Asia Category:2010s in Taiwan Category:Earthquakes in Taiwan Category:February 2016 events
